data.title: West Chester University
data.meta_description: West Chester University, located in southeastern PA, is a public, regional institution committed to high-quality undergraduate, graduate, and doctoral programs.
data.text:
Video description (this video does not have audio) for the video above:

Scene 1: Drone footage. Walking height moving towards 3 students that are sitting in front of a large fountain area. Water bubbling up is only a few inches.

Scene 2: Drone footage. A tightrope is extended between two trees at about a foot off the ground. The student is walking across the tightrope while other people watch. As the camera pulls back, you can see students walking down the sidewalk.

Scene 3: Drone footage. Two students sitting on a blanket on the grass. The camera goes past the students and towards a building.

Scene 4: Drone footage. Outside of Anderson Hall. Two bikes are parked at a bike rack and students are walking into the building. The camera moves forward and up.

Scene 5: A potted plant hanging gently blowing in the breeze. Philips is in the background.

Scene 6: Out of focus flowers in the foreground. In the background are students walking from left to right in front of a building which is in the background.

Scene 7: Drone footage. A student sitting in a chair on the grass with Philips in the background and preparing to do school work. Camera maintains focus and turns to the right.

Scene 8: The fountain at Rosedale Avenue and High Street.
